{"type":null,"faqId":49483,"title":"通过 WPS 连接 WLAN","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.20833333in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:13pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s3{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"通过 WPS 连接 WLAN\"XE \"WPS PIN 连接\"XE \"WPS 按钮连接\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>背景信息</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>您可以使用 WPS（WLAN Protected Setup，快速安全设置）功能来简化手机连接 WLAN 的操作。按下 WPS 按钮或者输入 PIN 码，即可将手机连接到具备 WPS 功能的 WLAN 路由器。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>操作步骤</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189787\" style=\"width:0.24583334in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span>点击 “WLAN”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 3  </span><span>点击 “WLAN” 开关，开启 WLAN。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 4  </span><span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189788\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; 高级设置”，您可以：</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“WPS 连接”，然后按下 WLAN 路由器上的 WPS 按钮。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“WPS PIN 码连接”，在 WLAN 路由器上输入手机生成的 PIN 码。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s3\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5227","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1447294484000,"seriesProductName":"KIW-AL10,KIW-CL00,KIW-TL00,KIW-TL00H,KIW-UL00","visitedTimes":56,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}